  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1619699">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1619699/" class="title-link">没剧情没场景没对白</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1619699"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/shelleytan/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1000541-41.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/shelleytan/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">口罩</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-01-14"
      class="main-meta">2009-01-14 22:41:23</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1619699_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  真的是自白，满篇絮絮叨叨重复着50字左右的阴谋论，除此之外，再无其他。没有看完。后悔买了。作者的认识水平比报刊专栏作家多不了多少，只是说了他们含糊其辞不愿说的话，而他却在变着方儿一遍遍重复。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1619699_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1619699_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
